          "context": {
            "markdown": "# Genoa G8 Clashes, 2001\n\nIn July 2001, Genoa became the site of mass protests during the G8 summit. Demonstrations, police raids, and street clashes left deep political scars and turned the city into a defining moment in the history of European protest. \n\n This website maps, in space, the most prominent photographs from those days."
          }
        }
      ]
