      "context": {
        "markdown": "A still from *Get Rid of Yourself (2003)*.\n\nA video-film tract built from footage shot during the 2001 Genoa G8 riots. Rather than a conventional documentary, the film pulls its images and sounds apart and recomposes them through disjunction, repetition, and cheap video effects to capture the intensity of a shared political experience."
